
Bash script to update the ip of an account on no-ip.com

How to use!

Configure the script with the correct username, password and hostname, make it executable (chmod +x) and run it (./noipupdater.sh)

Tips!

Place this in your cron file: 

*/5 * * * * cd /dir/where/file/is/ && /dir/where/file/is/noipupdater.sh

This will run the script every five minutes

Happy updating!!